text: Jan 25 12, try this Lai yuan next to CPF JCube. For $3.90 cannot complain, noodle enough for 2 mouthful, no meats except a few slices of liver and a meat ball. Overall acceptable.
Minced pork noodle came with 1 meatball and no minced meat except some floating traces in the soup. The noodles with sauce tastes good though.

Very poor ingredients and no meat at all.

Only liver. and 1 meatball. Noodles also not very good.

Pathetic portion for the price paid.

Ordered a few times but always give wrong orders. Today is probably my last straw. The meekia are more like half size meepok. The minced pork is mixed in the soup forcing you to drink the whole soup or carefully scoop and drain it to eat the ingredients.
Rude attitude. Worst customer service. We asked for food , he didnt even respond . Its like he is paying for our food . If you are hungry dont come here go to india, it will be more fast.
